name: HAWK VIEW
description:
HAWK VIEW is a generative experimental art inspired by architecture and urban development. The model is represented as a vector file of 16,364 individual lines. 

This 1/1 unique NFT comes with the original line drawing on 11”x17” paper (27.9cm x 49.6cm), Smooth Bristol 100 lb. (270 g/m²). Plotted with AxiDraw SE/A3.

International shipping included. 
Contact me via email at gwenael@lebodic.net to arrange shipment. 

Upon resale, original paper line drawing shall be sent to the new owner. Shipping covered by the new owner.

Digital version: PNG, 3300x5100px, 300dpi

Developed by Gwenaël Le Bodic with the Go programming language.
